  "projectRoot": "/workspaces/FeedbackFlow-AI",
  "projectName": "FeedbackFlow AI",
  "projectDescription": "Automated micro-SaaS to ingest, analyze, and triage real-world B2B/B2C public reviews using LLMs. Pulls in real customer feedback from a public source (GitHub Issues API), runs a multi-task LLM analysis on each item (sentiment, topics, severity, summary), stores the raw + structured results in Postgres, and presents a dashboard + inbox + detail UI for Product Managers and Customer Success teams to triage it.",
